The most amazing meal of my life. Each bite was another adventure! Our server was full of energy and extremely welcoming. We told her what we like and what we dont like and she took it from there. She brought out a series about 10 courses, each one a delicious surprise. It is extremely difficult to pick a favorite but if I had to it would be the tiny eel sandwich. It just melts in your mouth. The steak tartare bite was also delicious and the passion fruit caipirinha oyster.
